{"tid":1549462,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"推上報！賤男打老婆搶仔爭人錢，打到個仔流晒血","createTime":"2019-09-07T10:24:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T10:48:10.000Z","uid":225098,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"29381d54e51757c1f025641af960fd05727a438e","tid":1549462,"uid":225098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T10:24:22.000Z","msg":"呢個賤男本身個名叫戴青，有黑社會背景，佢成日打佢前妻，所以佢前妻頂唔順就同佢離婚帶埋個仔走，佢好爛賭又成日叫雞，冇錢就問我借，借咗好多，成一萬億。佢前妻離開咗佢之後生活更加好，養大咗個仔，個仔好叻，做咗金融才俊好揾得錢都好孝順。之後個賤男見到個仔咁叻有啲後悔，佢改咗個名叫鍾恭，冇端端上佢前妻屋企打個仔，之後仲逼佢前妻交返個仔俾佢，否則殺佢全家。咁佢前妻驚咗就交返個仔出嚟。喺個賤男威脅之下個仔讓咗間屋俾佢住。雖然個仔好唔妥呢個生父，但佢都忍咗一陣，但個賤男當正自己係一家之主，乜都管住曬，喺屋企裝cam睇住個仔一舉一動，連個仔着咩衫都要管，攤大手板問佢攞錢，但淨係俾50尺範圍個仔用嚟瞓覺，個仔一有意見就打佢，又用胡椒噴個仔塊面。個仔終於頂唔順，每日返到屋企都帶住頭盔同埋防毒面罩，驚俾賤男打，果然賤男仲搵埋佢個黑社會兄弟，佢兄弟叫江敬，打到佢成隻眼流晒血，成身刀傷，個仔就走過嚟揾我：「Sam叔，我爸爸好恐怖，你快啲嚟我屋企幫下我！」佢講完之後我醒起呢條撚樣爭我一萬億喎，咁我同佢對質，佢老味臭閪話戴青呢個人唔係佢！仲有仲有，佢成日性騷擾一條台灣妹，係咁逼人同佢扑嘢如果唔肯就打鳩佢，不過個台灣妹個男朋友好似好大隻所以佢唔夠膽郁手<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>還錢呀仆街！</strong></span>"},{"pid":"13594384040925254ca1a971c7bfd3f78ca9c6b9","tid":1549462,"uid":225098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T10:24:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://big5.www.gov.cn/gate/big5/www.gov.cn/xinwen/2019-05/08/5389743/images/dab22504b290409380e382137b9338cc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbig5.www.gov.cn%2Fgate%2Fbig5%2Fwww.gov.cn%2Fxinwen%2F2019-05%2F08%2F5389743%2Fimages%2Fdab22504b290409380e382137b9338cc.jpg&h=2e25bfe9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">認撚住呢條撚樣食屎狗鍾恭</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"24b1994357c65729ea02f6102219ec91a3be551f","tid":1549462,"uid":225098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T10:25:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20190613/s00006/022a23e3aefa0731af5d952168c2ed70.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20190613%2Fs00006%2F022a23e3aefa0731af5d952168c2ed70.jpg&h=473bb625&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢個仔好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ea988ff8406c55ade70931df975778be4023e36","tid":1549462,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T10:26:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5924d0de3c94e2a6b177a9d64c70188aba10a459","tid":1549462,"uid":225098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T10:27:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">還錢呀仆街！<br />\n一萬億美金！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"f61ab374bef829b159ba2da72bf249e36b4e4660","tid":1549462,"uid":225098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T10:28:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">還錢呀仆街！<br />\n一萬億美金！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"0d12398d4ee9971050f6bae45ee40f91934ab83f","tid":1549462,"uid":193293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T10:32:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5d36754b3854122036ce7e6ef81ed9e0f7fb2796","tid":1549462,"uid":225098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T10:33:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">還錢呀仆街！<br />\n一萬億美金！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"d673b1c93f7ac91fee1933aeeee6f8cc044fc915","tid":1549462,"uid":225098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T10:33:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">還錢呀仆街！<br />\n一萬億美金！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"9669aaa82f196711e22dd74bd778fa8e9e7dcddc","tid":1549462,"uid":254558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T10:34:13.000Z","msg":"元朗9.9七點半有人鏈<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a hr